name: First Visit! Air Canada New Livery 787-9 Dreamliner [C-FRSR] Landing at Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
On May 15th, Air Canada received its first Boeing 787-9 Dreamliner in their new livery in the form of C-FRSR, fin 848. It was delivered to Toronto after outfitting in Kansas City, and then flew YYZ-LHR the next day. Its second ever revenue flight is seen here, flying LHR-YYC, and is also YYC's first visit of a 789 in the new livery! Enjoy this brand new Dreamliner with ATC!

Thanks for watching!
